            <pb n="3" facs="#f0001"/>
            <div n="1">
                <head>
                    <hi rendition="#k">Baron Humboldt.</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The Berlin papers<lb break="yes"/>publish the following letter;</p>
                <lb break="yes"/>
                <p>@Overwhelmed by a correspondence which<lb break="yes"/>daily increases, and which averages yearly be-<lb break="no"/>tween 1,600 and 2,000 letters, pamphlets on<lb break="yes"/>subjects I know nothing in the world about,<lb break="yes"/>MSS. about which my advice is asked,<lb break="yes"/>schemes of emigration and colonization,<lb break="yes"/>models, machines, specimens of natural his-<lb break="no"/>tory, questions about balloons, requests for<lb break="yes"/>autographs, offers of services as my nurse, to<lb break="yes" />amuse me, &#x0026;c., &#x0026;c., &#x0026;c., I try once more<lb break="yes" />publicly to invite all my well-wishers to try<lb break="yes"/>and keep people from busying themselves<lb break="yes"/>about me on both continents, and from treat-<lb break="no"/>ing my house like an intelligence office; that<lb break="yes"/>despite the diminution of my physical and<lb break="yes" />intellectual strength, I may have a little leis-<lb break="no"/>ure and repose in which to labor. I hope<lb break="yes"/>this appeal (I have determined to make it<lb break="yes"/>with reluctance) will not be malevolently in-<lb break="no"/>terpreted.&#x2019;</p>
            </div>
            <lb break="yes"/>
        </body>
